    "title": "Marketplace Manager - FabAlley - Multiple Openings",
    "description": "FabAlley invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Marketplace Manager at our Aurangabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout FabAlley:\nFabAlley is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FabAlley!",
